{"tid":381530,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇依家啲學校整埋 App 俾家長睇仔女幾時返學放學？","createTime":"2017-08-31T04:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T06:43:54.000Z","uid":1772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f0a6d0ae77c77f5ec5864867988f685b01ee83e6","tid":381530,"uid":1772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:37:20.000Z","msg":"頭先上 App Store 碌碌下見到，專俾家長用<br />\n睇通告，簽通告可能真係方便左嘅，又環保啲<br />\n但見佢有埋返學放學時間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好慶幸唔係哩個世代讀書<br />\n俾人 check 住哂真係會覺得好大壓力、無哂自由<br />\n啲怪獸家長肯定見個仔女遲到少少、準時放但又遲返屋企會問長問短<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/122304_f3c0a7e476bb03d33f3ab5fbdb6e4c67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F122304_f3c0a7e476bb03d33f3ab5fbdb6e4c67.jpg&h=0b59c180&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"669e3b6b4ca7a320f52ff832e557a2b85e7bbc39","tid":381530,"uid":115040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:40:33.000Z","msg":"個個都自己down啦"},{"pid":"3f990b22bf0303712f11988504c4ae50a11e83b3","tid":381530,"uid":9708,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:43:06.000Z","msg":"如果當仔女狗咁養 的確係利多過弊"},{"pid":"74d1d3dd641deac4717f860a192ff42420ac11f2","tid":381530,"uid":29781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:47:15.000Z","msg":"我中學等車遲咗10分鐘返屋企都俾老母問餐死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80438b778311a7a3e90cf384b274f482ec962b30","tid":381530,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T04:48:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"23a9f4dea6a33ffc17519df730165c2ba626b62e","tid":381530,"uid":1772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:36:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前試過考完試 去網吧打機 之後同呀媽講正常時間放學<br />\n<br />\n宜家咁搞D學生好慘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放學即刻返屋企無哂樂趣"},{"pid":"45514e6cd3d5d37a588a57e5818be219476af729","tid":381530,"uid":93202,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:43:54.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n以前一定係昆老母要留係學校有咩課後活動之類<br />\n跟住同班同學打機 周圍流連<br />\n咁撚樣先係中學回憶黎"}]}